{
  "texts": [
    "Some elements such as neighborhood properties, user account metadata, content trends and relationships among accounts sharing the same type of information are key for improving detection mechanisms.",
    "Another strategy to improve the detection would be to concentrate in a small portion of data.",
    "This can be referring to a specific area or country, language, or topic.",
    "In this sense, meaningful information can be obtained more easily, especially if network interactions and group characterization are expected to be analyzed.",
    "Finally, vast research has been carried out over the Twitter platform, due to its inherent features, and with strong focus on text content analysis through Natural Language Processing (NLP) (Kanakaraj and Guddeti 2015)."
  ]
}